id, name, (
6371 * acos (
cos ( radians(-7.3695232) )
* cos( radians( lat ) )
* cos( radians( lng ) - radians(109.9071488) )
+ sin ( radians(-7.3695232) )
* sin( radians( lat ) )
)
) AS distance
FROM district_locations
HAVING distance < 3
ORDER BY distance
